         <abstract>
            <p>For appropriately adapted mesh-refinements, optimal order error estimates are proved for the finite element approximate solution of the Neumann problem for the second-order elliptic equation $Lu = \delta$, where $\delta$ is the Dirac distribution.</p>
          </abstract>
